profile_positions.description:
Main Responsibilities:
-Responsible Area: Far East, Mediterranean and Africa;
-Accept new bookings (Ocean/Ocean, Door/Ocean Inland Haulage);
-Monitor pending bookings and solve issues (allocation, freight issues, contract filings);
-In close contact with different stakeholders (Sales, Business Coordination Centre and Customer) to ensure that each booking can be confirmed towards customers as fast as possible;
-Focal Point for questions related to bookings and Inland Trucking.
